	   <tr><td colspan=2>A few boxes down, this newbie mage (I'm assuming) asked if Magicians should group or not. And I think Mages are definitely a perfect fit inbetween clerics and warriors in the term of a good group. And pets aren't supposed to tank directly in groups, but with a few mage pets in a group including a few Damage Shield here and there, Mages are invaluable for a good group.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
